    <div class="main review-item" id="2841828">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2841828/" class="title-link">书籍永远不是比较出来的——献给《明朝》和《宋...</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2841828"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/skidrow/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1294749-15.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/skidrow/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">贫民窟主-土</span>
    </a>  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-12-11"
      class="main-meta">2009-12-11 01:29:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2841828_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  　　宋史是宋史，明史是明史，有个鸟关系。  　　非要拿来比，有意思么？  　　难道因为馒头长得像包子，就非要说你个实心馒头肚子里什么都没有还要装得跟包子一样肚子里有货而显得有文化么？  　　  　　  　　  　　不可否认，在当年明月蹿红的同时，无数的“当年明月”迅速...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2841828/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
